I need to build a custom rating stepper in SwiftUI (1-5 stars). VoiceOver should let users adjust the value by swiping up/down:

```swift
struct RatingStepper: View {
    @Binding var rating: Int
    var body: some View {
        HStack {
            ForEach(1...5, id: \.self) { i in
                Image(systemName: i <= rating ? "star.fill" : "star")
                    .onTapGesture { rating = i }
            }
        }
    }
}
```
